n8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f7f2e151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"27ec7c1a4391725f947b65cae994d5a69c7db67b","tid":2107253,"uid":202898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"求其啦 反正未必有人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道左都未必有人想理"},{"pid":"e215c8c392c7edcdbd10949ceae1b228bd160dd8","tid":2107253,"uid":345160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27ec7c1a4391725f947b65cae994d5a69c7db67b","tid":2107253,"uid":202898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"求其啦 反正未必有人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道左都未必有人想理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"你講得啱 佢哋知嗰日我諗我已經唔係呢個世界"},{"pid":"dcaa853ddf5360ef45fa4aa89866e01693aeaa3a","tid":2107253,"uid":202898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e215c8c392c7edcdbd10949ceae1b228bd160dd8","tid":2107253,"uid":345160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27ec7c1a4391725f947b65cae994d5a69c7db67b","tid":2107253,"uid":202898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"求其啦 反正未必有人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道左都未必有人想理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"你講得啱 佢哋知嗰日我諗我已經唔係呢個世界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"你諗真d其實果d人只係垃圾 會開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8460da1a94f3abe124ae01b38ff8758b63607517","tid":2107253,"uid":112692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"知道既人又多左一個"},{"pid":"9e1c697615cc016a82ee32e031d9fe2293544012","tid":2107253,"uid":209026,"like":0,"di